    <h2>Excel calculators v2.0</h2>
    <p>
      Originally, Asahi representatives used a calculator developed in Excel that allowed them to calculate margins and prices based on sell price and discount.
    </p>
    <p>
      We've implemented the same principle for our calculator, but this one will also allow you to use the margin/price as a starting point or as and end point.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every calculator will change it's variables based on the type of drink and quantity selected, and there are different calculators for keg and pack sales.
